      <level>
        <content>
          <p><b>DEPARTMENT FOR INFRASTRUCTURE</b><b> Area to be abandoned </b><b>DEPARTMENT FOR INFRASTRUCTUREMap No. IN1/17/  referred to in “The Meadow Lane, Portadown  (Abandonment) Order (Northern Ireland) 2017” made by the Department on</b><marker name="tab" /><b>                        2017 and coming into operation on </b><marker name="tab" /><marker name="tab" /><b> </b><marker name="tab" /><b>2017. ©Based upon the Ordnance Survey map with the Permission of the Director and the Chief Executive. </b><b>Crown Copyright</b><marker name="tab" /><marker name="tab" /><marker name="tab" /><marker name="tab" /><b>SCALE 1:1250</b><b>Crown Copyright</b><marker name="tab" /><b>SCALE 1:200</b><marker name="tab" /><b> Area to be abandoned </b><b>DEPARTMENT FOR INFRASTRUCTUREMap No. IN1/17/  referred to in “The Glenwood Green, Dunmurry (Abandonment) Order (Northern Ireland) 2017” made by the Department on</b><marker name="tab" /><b>                        2017 and coming into operation on </b><marker name="tab" /><marker name="tab" /><b> </b><marker name="tab" /><b>2017. ©Based upon the Ordnance Survey map with the Permission of the Director and the Chief Executive. </b><b>Crown Copyright</b><marker name="tab" /><marker name="tab" /><marker name="tab" /><marker name="tab" /><b>SCALE 1:1250</b><b>Crown Copyright</b><marker name="tab" /><b>SCALE 1:200</b><marker name="tab" /><b> Area to be abandoned </b><b>DEPARTMENT FOR INFRASTRUCTURE</b><b>Map No. IN1/17/  referred to in “The Galway Drive, Belfast (Abandonment) Order (Northern Ireland) 2017” made by the Department on</b><marker name="tab" /><b>                        2017 and coming into operation on </b><marker name="tab" /><marker name="tab" /><b> </b><marker name="tab" /><b>2017. </b><b>©Based upon the Ordnance Survey map with the Permission of the Director and the Chief Executive. </b><b>Crown Copyright</b><marker name="tab" /><b>SCALE 1:1250</b><marker name="tab" /><b> </b><b>DEPARTMENT FOR INFRASTRUCTURE</b><b>Map No. IN1/19/114134 referred to in “The Railway Avenue, Newry (Abandonment) Order (Northern Ireland) 2020” made by the Department on 18th August 2020 and coming into operation on 7th October 2020.</b><b>©Based upon the Ordnance Survey map with the Permission of the Director and the Chief Executive.</b><b>Crown Copyright</b><marker name="tab" /><marker name="tab" /><marker name="tab" /><b>SCALE 1:1250</b><b> </b><b>Area to be abandoned</b></p>
        </content>
