      <level>
        <content>
          <p>Map No. IN1/17/  referred to in “The Academy Street, Belfast (Abandonment) Order (Northern Ireland) 2017” made by the Department on<marker name="tab" />                        2017 and coming into operation on <marker name="tab" /><marker name="tab" /> <marker name="tab" />2017. </p>
